csvIO

Class CSVHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • csvIO.CSVHelper

  • public class CSVHelper
extends Object
    https://raw.githubusercontent.com/agilepro/mendocino/master/src/com/purplehillsbooks/streams/CSVHelper.java Helps to read and write a CSV file, all methods are static writeLine: Converts list of String values into a line of a CSV file parseLine: read a line from a LineNumberReader and return the list of Strings That should be all you need. Create or open the file and streams yourself from whatever source you need to read from.. Everything in this class works on characters, and not bytes.
